{"type": "article", "id": 10290, "title": "James 管家家具", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-02T07:15:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235419A20DIPRqQj76UiG8.png", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p2\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">比利时设计师 Linde Hermans 最近推出了一个叫做 “James 管家”的系列产品，取“管家”是因为产品的设计试图把旧时管家的角色承担起来。一个扫帚作为整个产品的底座，扫帚把手变形后一个作为衣架，同时还承担着边桌的作用，看上去就像一个边打扫卫生边接过衣物的管家一样。这是<a href=\"http://www.lindehermans.be/james.html\" target=\"_blank\"> Linde Hermans 的主页</a>，点击可以查看更多作品。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235417ENx9HF1AJVzZDmwB.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.50694444\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235417iUSIX0P9bKO84VkD.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.50692042\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235418cUBp0wFYeTrI6Gyj.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.48355263\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235418suIwVdqeoJEm2ZiN.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.50553506\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235418pK8GO2LixT40oN5z.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"p3\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}